Get Predictions in CRM Analytics Dataflows
Use the prediction transformation in CRM Analytics dataflows to populate CRM Analytics datasets with predictions. Einstein calculates and saves predicted outcomes on a row-by-row basis. The prediction transformation requires a deployed model.

To view predictions, users must have the View Einstein Discovery Recommendations permission assigned to their Salesforce account. 

Configure predictions and improvements in dataflows: See prediction Transformation.
title: Configuring Predictions in CRM Analytics Dataflows
